Subject: [PATCH] ASoC: SOF: Revert: "core: unregister clients and machine drivers in .shutdown"
Mime-version: 1.0
Content-type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-transfer-encoding: 8bit
Git-commit: 44fda61d2bcfb74a942df93959e083a4e8eff75f
